{"arkId":"cl010436941","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010436941","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Cam\u00e9e mont\u00e9 : Les \u00e2ges de l\u0027amour","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Cam\u00e9e mont\u00e9 : Les \u00e2ges de l\u0027amour"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1825 - 1850","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 555 - Biennais, Vitrine table","room":"Salle 555, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1825,"endYear":1850,"imprecision":"","text":"2e quart du XIXe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Saulini, Tommaso","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"Attribu\u00e9 \u00e0","dates":[{"date":"1784","place":"Civitella di Subiaco","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1864","place":"Rome","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""},{"label":"Thorvaldsen, Bertel","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"D\u0027apr\u00e8s","dates":[{"date":"1770","place":"","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1844","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q47812"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"RFML.OA.2019.2.1","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"},{"value":"OA 12936","type":"Autre num\u00e9ro d\u0027inventaire"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"cam\u00e9e(s)","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Ce cam\u00e9e sur coquille reproduit un bas-relief de Thorvaldsen repr\u00e9sentant les \u00e2ges de l\u0027amour, librement inspir\u00e9e de la fresque antique \u0022Marchande d\u0027amours\u0022 .\r\nCette all\u00e9gorie des diff\u00e9rents \u00e2ges de l\u0027amour se lit de droite \u00e0 gauche. A droite, deux fillettes : la plus petite soul\u00e8ve avec curiosit\u00e9 le voile recouvrant la cage renfermant les amours, tandis que la plus grande caresse la t\u00eate d\u0027un amour se hissant hors de la cage. Psych\u00e9 assise a remplac\u00e9 la marchande de la fresque antique. Elle donne un amour \u00e0 une jeune fille agenouill\u00e9e qui lui tend les bras avec empressement. Plus tard, une femme aux formes plus pleines embrasse avec volupt\u00e9 l\u0027amour qu\u0027elle tient dans ses bras, puis vient le d\u00e9senchantement : une femme m\u00fbre, debout, tient avec indiff\u00e9rence et lassitude \u00e0 bout de bras un amour, tandis qu\u0027un homme assis semble accabl\u00e9 par le poids de l\u0027amour juch\u00e9 sur son dos. Enfin le vieillard tend le bras avec nostalgie vers un amour en vol qui semble le narguer.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"5,8","displayDimension":"5,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"13","displayDimension":"13 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau\/Technique : or, perles et rubis (encadrement) et vermeil (arri\u00e8re de la monture)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : or\r\nMat\u00e9riau : rubis\r\nMat\u00e9riau : vermeil = argent dor\u00e9\r\nTechnique : taille en cam\u00e9e (techniques pierre\/ciment\/pl\u00e2tre\/cire-\u003Etaill\u00e9 = taille)","placeOfCreation":"Rome (Italie-\u003ELatium)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Don M. Vittorio Magagnini, 2019","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don manuel","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date d\u0027affectation","value":"06\/02\/2019","startYear":2019,"endYear":2019},{"type":"d